---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---

<Layout
	lang="ro"
	title="Despre noi - Smarteye"
	description="Istoricul Smarteye si cateva dintre companiile care au ales solutiile noastre."
>
	<SiteHeader lang="ro" />
	<main class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Despre noi</h1>
			<div class="card history">
				<h2>Scurt istoric</h2>
				<p>
					SmartEye si-a inceput activitatea in 1994, sub numele de Elka Security, fiind printre
					primele companii din Romania specializate in productia si instalarea sistemelor de alarma
					antiefractie.
				</p>
				<p>
					Pornind de la un mic atelier, compania si-a extins constant serviciile catre
					supraveghere video, control acces, interfonie, automatizari si alte solutii tehnice.
				</p>
				<p>
					Din 2008, ramura SmartEye Surveillance Solutions din Bucuresti s-a concentrat pe proiecte
					de supraveghere pentru segmentul small & medium business.
				</p>
			</div>

			<section class="section clients">
				<h2>Clienti</h2>
				<div class="grid">
					<article class="card">Mega Image</article>
					<article class="card">La Placinte</article>
					<article class="card">Havi Logistics</article>
					<article class="card">Nextgen</article>
					<article class="card">Ogilvy Romania</article>
					<article class="card">Luk-Oil Romania</article>
					<article class="card">SNR Radiocom</article>
					<article class="card">Conpet S.A. Ploiesti</article>
					<article class="card">Federatia Romana de Tenis</article>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</main>
	<SiteFooter lang="ro" />
</Layout>

<style>
	.history {
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.clients {
		padding-bottom: 0;
	}
</style>
